sentence.text: epidermis development and keratinization (KRT6A, KRT6B AAAAA KRT6C) gene expression was assessed in publically available serous ovarian cancer data sets, ovarian cancer cell lines and primary serous ovarian cancer cells.

Survival analyses showed that high epidermis development mRNA in stage III/IV serous ovarian cancers was significantly associated with reduced progression-free (HR 1.38, P AAAA 0.0001) and overall survival (HR 1.28, P = 0.013) whilst high keratinization mRNA was only associated with reduced progression-free survival (HR 1.2, P = 0.031).
epidermis development but not keratinizationC mRNA expression was increased in chemotherapy resistant primary serous ovarian cancer cells compared to chemotherapy sensitive cells.
